He described Chekov as an odd character, being a Russian who was brought on to the show "in the middle of the Cold War".
He recalled a "scene where they're talking to Apollo [who says], 'I am Apollo.
' And Chekov is like, 'And I am the czar of all Russias.
' [...] They gave him these lines.
I mean he really is the weirdest, weirdest character".
